(X_t)_{t\geq 0}
n\in\mathbb{N}
(X_t^n)_{t\geq 0}
 X_t^n(\omega)=X_{i/2^n}(\omega)\quad \text{if } \tfrac{i-1}{2^n}\leq t<\tfrac{i}{2^n}\; \text{and } i\geq 1. 
